IMAPAccount icloud
Host imap.mail.me.com
Port 993
User salsarray@icloud.com
PassCmd "gpg -q --decrypt ~/.mutt/icloud-pass.ggp"
TLSType IMAPS

IMAPStore icloud-remote
Account icloud

MaildirStore icloud-local
Path ~/Mail/iCloud/
Inbox ~/Mail/iCloud/Inbox
Trash ~/Mail/iCloud/Deleted\ Messages
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel icloud
Far :icloud-remote:
Near :icloud-local:
Patterns *
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *
Sync Pull
